stories.text: AsposeApp provides free file format apps that can smoothly handle the most common documents types. It fully supports online File Processing for PDF, MS Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Visio, MS Project, OneNote, OpenOffice, CAD drawings, 3D formats and many more. You can easily convert Word documents to JPG, PDF, HTML and other formats, upload and convert Excel & Calc spreadsheet formats, PowerPoint PPT, PPTX & OpenOffice ODP presentation formats to industry-standard formats, image conversion to PDF, Photoshop PSD, JPG, GIF, PNG, BMP, TIFF and so on. It also allows viewing, extracting and converting Outlook PST, OST & MBOX, MSG, EML files with ease.  Moreover, you can view, edit, merge, split or unlock documents, generate reports, extract text and images, add signature or watermark and much more.
